visual.name: TextEnhancerByMAQSoftware
visual.description: Text Enhancer transforms a plain Power BI text into various styling formats, which can be used for rich UI reporting purpose. It basically has all features as the text editor of Microsoft PowerPoint.

alignment.description: Change the horizontal alignment of text.

alignmentV.description: Change the vertical alignment of text.

textIndent.description: Change the indentation of text by pixels.

lineIndent.description: Change the indentation of text by pixels.

textRotate.description: Rotate the text by specified angle in degrees.

perspective.description: Define how far the object is away from the user. A lower value will result in a more intensive 3D effect than a higher value.

lineHeight.description: Change the spacing between multiple lines.

skewX.description: Skew the text by specified angle in degrees, along the X-Axis.

skewY.description: Skew the text by specified angle in degrees, along the Y-Axis.

showColon.description: Display a colon between Static & Dynamic Text.

textPosition.description: Position the static text as a prefix or suffix.

textTransform.description: Change the case of letters in static text.

textShadowColor.description: Change color of static text shadow.

backgroundcolor.description: Change background color of static text.

transparency.description: Change transparency level of static text highlighter.

boldStyle.description: Change the static text to bold.

italicStyle.description: Change the static text to italics.

backgroundcolor.description: Change background color of dynamic text.

transparency.description: Change transparency level of dynamic text highlighter.

textTransform.description: Change the case of letters in dynamic text.

textShadowColor.description: Change color of dynamic text shadow.

boldStyle.description: Change the dynamic text to bold.

italicStyle.description: Change the dynamic text to italics.
